comment: The signature-permutation of the automorphism which is derived from the first non-recursive automorphism *A069770 with recursion schema NEPEED (see A122284 for the definition), or equivalently, derived from the fifteenth non-recursive automorphism *A089859 with recursion schema KROF (see A122202 for the definition).
